Susan Monica was found guilty on Tuesday of murdering two handymen on her pig farm in 2012 and 2013 . 
  She was sentenced to a minimum of 50 years in prison . 
  The remains of Stephen Delicino and Robert Haney were found on her farm . 
  Monica admitted to killing the men and feeding their bodies to her pigs . 
  She said she shot them in self-defense after she found them being attacked by her pigs  . 
 